title: Static Analysis

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.description: Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.

"aatkit_cmp_explanation_1" : "Thank you for downloading this app. By continuing to use this app, you confirm that you have read, understand and accept the terms and conditions as well as the privacy policy. This app shows ads in order to remain free.

To improve your experience, the app uses advertising IDs and other analytics. Selected partners may access and use information about your device to provide relevant and personalized ads. The purposes of data use include information storage and access, personalization, ad selection, delivery and reporting, content selection, delivery and reporting, measurement as well as matching data to offline sources, linking devices, precise geographic location data. You can learn more about your choices by selecting “Details”. You can change your mind and review your choice at any time by accessing the privacy settings of the app. Please help us to run this app and select “Agree”."
"aatkit_cmp_explanation_2" : "More partners are asking for your consent for the purposes mentioned above"

"appconsent_inf_body" : "The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) governs the use of personal data by companies.

Personal data is any data that is attached to a person's identity (name, contact details, browsing history, etc…)."

"appconsent_inf_p_body" : "Consent under the DGMP must be:
- freely given
- for a precise and explicit purpose
- unambiguous
- subject to the right of withdrawal
- subject to the right of portability"

"appconsent_inf_subbody" : "This protection measure, which came into force on 25 May 2018, is mandatory and gives everyone the power to control their own information when navigating the digital channels.

All citizens of the European Union must authorise or refuse the collection and processing of their personal data for a specific purpose by a company."

"appconsent_p_2_d" : "This is a collection and analysis of your behaviour and actions when using our services (website or applications) in order to subsequently personalize the advertising and/or content that will be offered to you in other contexts."

This does not include the customization of advertising."

"appconsent_p_4_d" : "This information is collected, combined with information previously collected on our media or other sources, to enable us to select and deliver content adapted to your profile (interests, geolocalizations…) and to measure its effectiveness. "aatkit_cmp_explanation_1" : "Vielen Dank für den Download der App. Durch die Nutzung dieser App, bestätigtst Du, dass Du die Allgemeinen Geschäftsbedingungen und die Datenschutzrichtlinien gelesen, verstanden und annerkannt hast. Damit diese App weiterhin gratis zur Verfügung gestelllt werden kann, wird in der App Werbung gezeigt.

Um die Nutzung der App zu verbessern, greift die App auf die Advertising ID und andere Kennungen Deines Gerätes zu. Ausgewählte Partner können auf diese Daten zugreifen, um für Dich relevante und personalisierte Werbung zu liefern. Aufgrund dieser Zwecke, werden Deine Daten genutzt: Speicherung und Zugriff auf Informationen, Personalisierung, Auswahl, Schaltung und Auswertung von Anzeigen, Auswahl, Schaltung und Auswertung von Inhalten, Bewertung sowie Abgleichen von Offline-Daten, Verknüpfen von Geräten, Präzise Geostandort-Daten. Weitere Auswahlmöglichkeiten erfährst Du unter "Details". Du kannst Deine Auswahl jederzeit in den Datenschutzeinstellungen der App ändern. Bitte unterstütze diese App und wähle "Zustimmen"."
"aatkit_cmp_explanation_2" : "Weitere Partner bitten um Deine Zustimmung zu den oben erwähnten Zwecken."

"appconsent_con_text1" : "Wir empfehlen Ihnen, die Erfassung Ihrer personenbezogenen Daten im Zusammenhang mit der Nutzung der Anwendung zu konfigurieren."

"appconsent_inf_body" : "Die Allgemeine Datenschutzverordnung (DGMP), auch bekannt als General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), regelt die Verwendung personenbezogener Daten durch Unternehmen.

Personenbezogene Daten sind alle Daten, die mit der Identität einer Person verknüpft sind (Name, Kontaktdaten, Browserverlauf, etc…)."

"appconsent_inf_subbody" : "Diese Schutzmaßnahme, die am 25. Mai 2018 in Kraft getreten ist, ist verbindlich und gibt jedem die Möglichkeit, beim Navigieren durch die digitalen Kanäle seine eigenen Informationen zu kontrollieren.

Alle Bürger der Europäischen Union müssen die Erhebung und Verarbeitung ihrer personenbezogenen Daten für einen bestimmten Zweck durch ein Unternehmen genehmigen oder ablehnen."
"appconsent_int_t1" : "Wir empfehlen Ihnen, die Erfassung Ihrer personenbezogenen Daten im Zusammenhang mit der Nutzung der Anwendung zu konfigurieren."

So können beispielsweise Ihr Smartphone, Tablett und Computer oder Ihre Geolokalisierungsdaten verbunden werden und die Kontinuität der Erkennung, auch offline und unabhängig von Ihrem Medium sichergestellt werden."

"appconsent_p_2_d" : "Dies ist eine Erfassung und Analyse Ihres Verhaltens und Ihrer Handlungen bei der Nutzung unserer Dienste (Website oder Applikation), um anschließend Werbung und/oder Inhalte zu personalisieren, die Ihnen in anderen Zusammenhängen angeboten werden."

"appconsent_p_3_d" : "Diese Informationen werden gemeinsam mit den Informationen gesammelt, die zuvor auf unseren Medien oder anderen Quellen erfasst wurden. Dies Ermöglicht es uns Anzeigen auszuwählen und zu liefern, die an Ihr Profil angepasst sind (Interessen, Geolokalisierung…) und deren Wirksamkeit zu messen. Dies schließt die Personalisierung der Werbung nicht ein."

"appconsent_p_4_d" : "Diese Informationen werden gemeinsam mit den Informationen gesammelt, die zuvor auf unseren Medien oder anderen Quellen erfasst wurden. "appconsent_inf_body" : "Le Règlement Général sur la Protection des Données (RGPD), appelé aussi General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), encadre l’usage des données personnelles par les entreprises.

Les données personnelles représentent toutes données étant attachées à l’identité d’une personne (nom, coordonnées, historique de navigation, etc…)."

"appconsent_inf_subbody" : "Cette mesure de protection, entrée en vigueur le 25 mai 2018, est obligatoire et donne à chacun le pouvoir de maîtriser les informations lui appartenant lors de la navigation sur Ies canaux digitaux.

Tous les citoyens de l’Union Européenne doivent autoriser ou refuser la collecte et le traitement de leurs données personnelles pour un usage déterminé par une entreprise."

playstore_details.title: Akinator
playstore_details.description:
Akinator can read your mind and tell you what character you are thinking of, just by asking a few questions. Think of a real or fictional character and Akinator will try to guess who it is. 
Will you dare challenge the genie? And what about other themes like movies, animals…?

###NEW###
2 ADDITIONAL THEMES BESIDES THE CHARACTERS
Akinator is getting stronger and stronger... The genie has increased his knowledge, and now you have the opportunity to also challenge him on movies and animals!
Will you manage to defeat Akinator?

GO IN SEARCH FOR AKI AWARDS
Akinator invites you to think outside the box. As you know, he likes to guess characters and to take on difficult challenges. To do that, make him guess forgotten characters who have not been played for a very long time and you may win the best Aki Awards.

BE THE BEST PLAYER
Challenge the other players on the leaderboards to prove who the best is. You may write your name on the Last Super Awards board or on the Hall of Fame. 

KEEP ON GUESSING
Each day, try to find the 5 mysterious characters and win some additional and specific Aki Awards. Complete the full Daily Challenge and earn the Gold Daily Challenge Aki Award, one of the most prestigious Aki Awards.

UNLEASH YOUR CREATIVITY
Using Geniz, you can unlock and play with new backgrounds and customize your genie to your liking. The genie will turn into a vampire, a cowboy or a disco man. Unleash your creativity by mixing 12 hats and 13 clothes to create your ideal combination.

PLAY MORE, WITHOUT ANY LIMITS!
THE ULTIMATE POTION unlocks all characters and removes all ads from the app, to ensure you get the best gaming experience.

Main features:
-16 languages (French, English, Spanish, Portuguese, German, Japanese, Arabic, Russian, Italian, Chinese, Turkish, Korean, Hebrew, Polish, Indonesian and Dutch)
-Get 2 additional themes: Movies and Animals
-Aki Awards Board to get an overview of your collection
-Hall of Fame with both current and previous ranking
-Last super awards for Black, Platinum and Gold Aki Awards
-Daily Challenges Board
-Add magic by proposing a photo or some questions
-Customize your genie by combining different hats and clothes
-Child filter to let the children play safely
-Video recording feature in-game

---------------------------
